node.text: @lizzie_fogarty90 canne wait x
Please go to Scran and Scallie in Edinburgh! Get the Marrow Pie YOU WILL LOVE!!!! P.s love you and your podcast 😘💞

Four in a bedroom these days ❤️ how did I not know about Malton before!! It's heaven! Even in the pouring rain. The most gorgeous town with amazing independent shops (shout out @kempsmalton ) the friendliest people and delightful food and bedrooms @thetalbotmalton ( third pic is a double cheese souffle 😍) EDINBURGH I AM REJUVENATED AND READY!;
@nofilternessie Edinburgh is mad busy already ❤️
I live 20 mins from Mallon and didn’t know this wonder was there! Desperately trying to get tix for Table Manners this weekend.
Beautiful
@captaincripps_
Where is the cook book, Jessie. I want your brothers lemon ice cream YESTERDAY.
@beckyllancaster *ahem*

I get married here in 5 weeks and you stayed in the bridal suite 😱 can’t believe on my wedding day I’m staying in the same room you did! 💃❤️ how lovely is the venue, we have fallen completely in love with Malton! Xx
We stayed there in February & attended the Cookery School.. fab foody heaven! 💕
Never heard of malton before. It looks fab. And that souflee look EPIC. I want one!!
That double cheese soufflé is giving me life! 💛💛💛
We love @malton it’s such a lovely market town 👏👏👏 I can’t wait to see the new Yorkshire Pudding recipe artwork in the market place 💕
@katherine_greene123 sounds like somewhere to add to your UK travels list
Fab! Just down the road from me. Love North Yorkshire 😊
@jessieware so pleased you found the fabulous @thetalbotmalton ❤️

Aww such a beautiful, beautiful place. Hope you’re making the most of lovely North Yorkshire. If you have time head to Castle Howard; the grounds are gorgeous. Although you might have to do a sundance 😀☀️xx
Argh @steph_hanahoe yessssss
Our local town! It’s the best, wish had been there to say ello xxx
@tprimarolo someone else shares your love for Malton 🤣🤣
@emptynestfor2 😍
Get the Yorkshire Pudding Pie!  In Yorkshire for Yorkshire Day 🥳❤️
So glad it was ok - well done David & @thetalbotmalton
@jessieware the soufflé! ❤️
In love 😍
